column2: SELECT sp.objid, sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.zErr, sp.modelMag_u, sp.modelMag_g, sp.modelMag_r, sp.modelMag_i, sp.modelMag_z, sp.modelMagErr_u, sp.modelMagErr_g, sp.modelMagErr_r, sp.modelMagErr_i, sp.modelMagErr_z FROM SpecPhoto sp JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) n  ON sp.objid=n.objid WHERE (sp.class=&&&)
